278
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:25,240
Hello? Hello?

279
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:29,760
Please help me. I don't know when 
this phone call will be disconnected.

280
00:21:31,150 --> 00:21:33,560
Hello? You are the one 
who called earlier, right?

281
00:21:33,560 --> 00:21:38,160
I'm currently locked in a casket.

282
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:41,640
On my way home... suddenly...

283
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:45,310
When I woke up, I was in here.

284
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:48,360
Please help me.

285
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:52,610
Please help me! Get me out of here!

286
00:21:52,610 --> 00:21:54,980
Please save me!

287
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:56,540
Save me!

288
00:21:56,540 --> 00:21:59,820
Miss, please calm down.

289
00:21:59,820 --> 00:22:01,890
Miss.

290
00:22:03,710 --> 00:22:06,610
Save me!

291
00:22:06,610 --> 00:22:07,860
Please save me!

292
00:22:07,860 --> 00:22:10,890
Mi Jin? Mi Jin?

293
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,410
Who are you?

294
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:18,270
How do you know my name?

295
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:20,460
I am Detective Seo Joon Yeong.

296
00:22:20,460 --> 00:22:24,150
Right now, our team is coming to save you,

297
00:22:24,150 --> 00:22:25,300
so don't cry.

298
00:22:25,300 --> 00:22:28,710
Can you slowly tell us what happened?

299
00:22:28,710 --> 00:22:32,800
Once I woke up, I was 
trapped in this casket.

300
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:37,510
I don't know who 
this phone belongs to.

301
00:22:37,510 --> 00:22:41,370
I got a call from some man

302
00:22:41,370 --> 00:22:44,450
and I don't know when this call will get disconnected either.

303
00:22:44,450 --> 00:22:46,590
I'm scared.

304
00:22:46,590 --> 00:22:50,810
Mi Jin, before this call ends, 
we will definitely be there to save you.

305
00:22:50,810 --> 00:22:52,030
I promise.

306
00:22:52,030 --> 00:22:55,870
Excuse me, my mom...

307
00:22:55,870 --> 00:22:59,530
Please contact my mom.

308
00:22:59,530 --> 00:23:02,890
My mom's name is Yoo Ji Won.

309
00:23:02,890 --> 00:23:08,010
- Dad's name is Lee Joon Hui. 
- The home number is...

310
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:14,410
I know the number.

311
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:17,800
All right, Mi Jin.
[Yoo Ji Won, Lee Joon Hui]

312
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:20,770
Your mom actually reported this.

313
00:23:20,770 --> 00:23:22,460
My mom did?
[GPS location is not available]

314
00:23:22,460 --> 00:23:24,550
My mom did?

315
00:23:24,550 --> 00:23:27,380
Mom! Mom...

316
00:23:27,380 --> 00:23:28,780
Senior.

317
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:30,560
Mom...

318
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:33,630
- The number doesn't show so it's not traceable.
- How about IMEI ?

319
00:23:33,630 --> 00:23:35,820
The IMEI is not captured either.

320
00:23:37,090 --> 00:23:40,890
Mi Jin, you said you got a 
call to that phone earlier, right?

321
00:23:40,890 --> 00:23:44,010
If the call comes in again, can you 
memorize the number and tell us?

322
00:23:44,010 --> 00:23:47,110
If we know the number, it'll 
help us to find the location.

323
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:48,460
Okay.

324
00:23:48,460 --> 00:23:51,140
All right. Thank you.

325
00:23:53,410 --> 00:23:56,560
[Yoo Ji Won. Lee Joon Hui]

326
00:23:56,560 --> 00:23:58,360
- Find them.
- Yes.

327
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:01,000
Is this all?

328
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:04,260
The files of 1997 and 1998 are missing!

329
00:24:04,260 --> 00:24:07,150
Bring everything related to Jo Pil Doo!

330
00:24:07,150 --> 00:24:09,190
- Connect her.
- Yes.

331
00:24:13,380 --> 00:24:14,190
Yes, Senior.

332
00:24:14,190 --> 00:24:15,830
Oh Ye Ji, it's Captain Lee.

333
00:24:15,830 --> 00:24:16,870
Yes, Captain.

334
00:24:16,870 --> 00:24:18,900
Okay, did you find out who the victim is?

335
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:23,570
I couldn't find out anything else yet except 
it's a 17-year-old female high school student.

336
00:24:24,430 --> 00:24:27,060
A 17-year-old female high school student.

337
00:24:27,060 --> 00:24:27,860
And?

338
00:24:27,860 --> 00:24:30,830
The suspect is using the same 
method as the case 20 years ago.

339
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:35,220
At an abandoned factory, she is 
buried alive in a 1.5-meter long casket.

340
00:24:35,220 --> 00:24:38,200
A person who can see 
people's deaths told them.

341
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:39,490
What?

342
00:24:39,490 --> 00:24:40,860
The thing is...

343
00:24:40,860 --> 00:24:45,100
Detective Seo Joon Yeong is the daughter of the 
detective who died during the arrest of Jo Pil Doo.

344
00:24:45,100 --> 00:24:46,680
We know that.

345
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:48,940
Wait.

346
00:24:48,940 --> 00:24:51,670
Don't tell me... Is  Seo Joon Yeong 
in charge of this case as well?

347
00:24:51,670 --> 00:24:53,420
Yes.

348
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:57,490
Okay. We got a rough outline.

349
00:24:57,490 --> 00:25:00,100
Hey, report to us as soon as you 
find out the victim's identity.

350
00:25:00,100 --> 00:25:01,760
Yes.

351
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:11,510
[A 17 year old female high school student.  The same method... ]

352
00:25:11,510 --> 00:25:14,830
A Jo Pil Doo copycat crime. 
Daughter following in father's footsteps.

353
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:17,650
Will Detective Seo Joon Yeong 
catch the culprit?

354
00:25:17,650 --> 00:25:20,290
Wow, the headline will be awesome!

355
00:25:20,290 --> 00:25:21,970
Everyone attention!

356
00:25:21,970 --> 00:25:25,580
We will be the first ones to report on this 
female student kidnapping case, no matter what.

357
00:25:25,580 --> 00:25:26,290
- Yes!
- Yes!

358
00:25:26,290 --> 00:25:29,460
We'll focus on Seo Joon Yeong 
for our first article's headline.

359
00:25:29,460 --> 00:25:32,920
As soon as we find out the victim's identity, 
put out articles with updates in real-time.

360
00:25:32,920 --> 00:25:35,570
- Okay?
- Yes!

361
00:25:47,460 --> 00:25:50,030
[Missing Person Report  By Yoo Ji Won]

