363
00:26:18,650 --> 00:26:21,620
I have no idea what's happening...

364
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:24,180
This isn't just a 
simple copycat crime.

365
00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:25,660
What do you mean?

366
00:26:25,660 --> 00:26:29,560
Student Lee Mi Jin... is 
Reporter Lee Joon Hui's daughter.

367
00:26:29,560 --> 00:26:32,160
Reporter Lee Joon Hui?

368
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:35,010
Lee Joon Hui, Reporter Lee Joon Hui...

369
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:37,790
The reporter that wrote your 
dad's articles 20 years ago?

