00:27:11,250 --> 00:27:14,110
If this is a situation that someone has to 
take responsibility for happening, I'll take it.

381
00:27:14,110 --> 00:27:16,290
- Joon Yeong!
- If there's a way to save her,

382
00:27:16,290 --> 00:27:18,590
