383
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:29,380
[Wife]

384
00:27:29,380 --> 00:27:30,740
Come here.

385
00:27:30,740 --> 00:27:34,200
Join Oh Ye Ji right now and cover Seo Joon Yeong.

386
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:38,290
Once they find out the location, they'll move to that place.  
So you stay very close to her and send us any pictures of the scene.

